urrent price from step 5, compute the final percentage difference: ((current - highest_close) / highest_close) * 100. Report all three required values.\", \"required_tool\": null, \"dependency_on_step\": [2, 5], \"uses_signal\": \"highest_close_date, highest_close_price\"}]",
